            ],
            "text": "(langsung memegang tangan {playerName}) Tidak. Kamu nggak pernah sendirian.",
            "next": "scene12_n019"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n019",
            "type": "narration",
            "text": "Rachel datang. Henry. Mike. Damian keluar dari kamar sambil memegang bahunya yang diperban.",
            "next": "scene12_n020"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n020",
            "type": "line",
            "speaker": "damian",
            "expression": "neutral",
            "characters": [
                {
                    "characterId": "damian",
                    "expression": "neutral",
                    "position": "center",
                    "isSpeaking": true
                }
            ],
            "text": "Kau masih punya kami.",
            "next": "scene12_n021"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n021",
            "type": "narration",
            "text": "{playerName} menatap mereka satu per satu. Lalu tersenyum. Untuk pertama kalinya, senyum itu bukan topeng.",
            "next": "scene12_n022"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n022",
            "type": "line",
            "speaker": "{playerName}",
            "expression": "smile",
            "characters": [
                {
                    "characterId": "damian",
                    "expression": "neutral",
                    "position": "center",
                    "isSpeaking": false
                },
                {
                    "characterId": "alaric",
                    "expression": "neutral",
                    "position": "left",
                    "isSpeaking": false
                }
            ],
            "text": "(tersenyum tipis) Jadi selama ini aku selalu berhalusinasi ya? Pantas saja dia selalu menghilang begitu saja.",
            "next": "scene12_n023"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n023",
            "type": "line",
            "speaker": "damian",
            "expression": "neutral",
            "characters": [
                {
                    "characterId": "damian",
                    "expression": "neutral",
                    "position": "center",
                    "isSpeaking": true
                }
            ],
            "text": "Mungkin sosok itu menghilang karena kini kamu sudah menyadari sesuatu.",
            "next": "scene12_n024"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n024",
            "type": "line",
            "speaker": "{playerName}",
            "expression": "neutral",
            "characters": [
                {
                    "characterId": "damian",
                    "expression": "neutral",
                    "position": "center",
                    "isSpeaking": false
                }
            ],
            "text": "Iya, aku baru menyadarinya sekarang, bahwa aku tidak pernah sendiri. Selalu ada kalian yang menjaga dan menemaniku. Maaf ya...",
            "next": "scene12_n025"
        },
        {
            "id": "scene12_n025",
            "type": "narration",
            "text": "Mereka semua saling berpelukan. Layar gelap.",
